{"id": "art-482", "label": "Art. 482", "title": "Art. 482: Promovarea în funcţia publică de conducere", "slug": "art-482", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_531771936\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1218\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_531771936\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 482:\nPromovarea în func&#355;ia public&#259; de conducere </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_117414930\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1217\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_117414930\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Promovarea în func&#355;ia public&#259; de conducere\neste modalitatea de dezvoltare a carierei unui func&#355;ionar public prin\nocuparea, în urma promov&#259;rii concursului, a unei func&#355;ii publice de\nconducere vacante, de acela&#351;i nivel sau de nivel superior celei\nde&#355;inute, potrivit ierarhiz&#259;rii prev&#259;zute la art. 390 alin. (1).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1897804783\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1216\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1897804783\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prin excep&#355;ie de la prevederile alin. (1), la\nconcursurile de promovare pot participa &#351;i func&#355;ionari publici care\nde&#355;in o func&#355;ie public&#259; de conducere de nivel superior celei\npentru care candideaz&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_486427\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1215\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_486427\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Concursul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1) se organizeaz&#259;\npe baza unui plan de promovare în func&#355;ii publice de conducere, elaborat\nde c&#259;tre Agen&#355;ia Na&#355;ional&#259; a Func&#355;ionarilor Publici\n&#351;i prin care se previzioneaz&#259;, pentru o perioad&#259; de 2 ani,\nnecesarul pentru ocupare prin promovare a unor func&#355;ii publice de\nconducere la nivelul autorit&#259;&#355;ilor &#351;i institu&#355;iilor publice\nîn cadrul c&#259;rora sunt stabilite func&#355;iile publice prev&#259;zute la\nart. 385 alin. (1) &#351;i (2), cu excep&#355;ia celor care beneficiaz&#259; de\nstatute speciale în condi&#355;iile legii. Planul de promovare în func&#355;ii\npublice de conducere se aprob&#259; prin hot&#259;rârea Guvernului\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 467 alin. (5). Informa&#355;iile necesare\nelabor&#259;rii planului de promovare în func&#355;ii publice de conducere,\nprecum &#351;i modalitatea de transmitere a acestora se aprob&#259; prin\nordinul pre&#351;edintelui Agen&#355;iei Na&#355;ionale a Func&#355;ionarilor\nPublici prev&#259;zut la art. 467 alin. (5).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1568098173\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1214\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1568098173\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cadrul\nconcursului de promovare în func&#355;iile publice de conducere prev&#259;zute\nla art. 385 alin. (1) &#351;i (2), cu excep&#355;ia celor care beneficiaz&#259;\nde statute speciale în condi&#355;iile legii, se verific&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_335770843\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1213\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_335770843\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)competen&#355;ele generale necesare ocup&#259;rii unei\nfunc&#355;ii publice de conducere;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1992190656\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1212\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1992190656\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)cuno&#351;tin&#355;ele de specialitate &#351;i\ncompeten&#355;ele specifice necesare ocup&#259;rii unei func&#355;ii publice de\nconducere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_345675227\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1211\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_345675227\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Competen&#355;ele\ngenerale prev&#259;zute la alin. (4) lit. a) se consider&#259; a fi îndeplinite\nde c&#259;tre func&#355;ionarii publici care la data depunerii dosarului de\nconcurs se afl&#259; în una dintre urm&#259;toarele situa&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1264134062\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1210\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1264134062\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)ocup&#259; o func&#355;ie public&#259; de conducere de\nacela&#351;i nivel sau o func&#355;ie public&#259; de conducere de nivel\nsuperior celei pentru care candideaz&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2059292092\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1209\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2059292092\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)au ocupat pentru o perioad&#259; de minimum 3 ani o\nfunc&#355;ie public&#259; de conducere de acela&#351;i nivel &#351;i/sau o\nfunc&#355;ie public&#259; de conducere de nivel superior celei pentru care\ncandideaz&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_594058883\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1208\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_594058883\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Func&#355;ionarii publici care nu se afl&#259; în\nsitua&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (5) dovedesc îndeplinirea\ncompeten&#355;elor generale prev&#259;zute la alin. (4) lit. a) prin promovarea\nunei probe de testare avansat&#259; organizat&#259; de Agen&#355;ia\nNa&#355;ional&#259; a Func&#355;ionarilor Publici în condi&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 50-53 din anexa nr. 10.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_633292140\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1207\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_633292140\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Verificarea cuno&#351;tin&#355;elor de specialitate\n&#351;i a competen&#355;elor specifice necesare ocup&#259;rii unei func&#355;ii\npublice de conducere se realizeaz&#259; prin concurs pe post organizat de\nautorit&#259;&#355;ile &#351;i institu&#355;iile publice prev&#259;zute la art.\n369 lit. a), c) &#351;i e), ai c&#259;ror conduc&#259;tori au competen&#355;a\nde numire în func&#355;ii publice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_37327685\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1206\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_37327685\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cadrul\nconcursului de promovare în func&#355;iile publice de conducere prev&#259;zute\nla art. 385 alin. (3) se verific&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_632356243\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1205\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_632356243\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)competen&#355;ele generale necesare ocup&#259;rii unei\nfunc&#355;ii publice de conducere;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_833801554\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1204\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_833801554\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)cuno&#351;tin&#355;ele de specialitate &#351;i\ncompeten&#355;ele specifice necesare ocup&#259;rii unei func&#355;ii publice de\nconducere, prin concurs pe post organizat de autorit&#259;&#355;ile &#351;i\ninstitu&#355;iile publice prev&#259;zute la art. 369 lit. b), ai c&#259;ror\nconduc&#259;tori au competen&#355;a de numire în func&#355;ii publice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1774913766\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1203\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1774913766\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Pentru verificarea îndeplinirii competen&#355;elor\ngenerale prev&#259;zute la alin. (8) lit. a), prevederile alin. (5) se\naplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1291259152\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1202\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1291259152\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Pentru verificarea de c&#259;tre autorit&#259;&#355;ile\n&#351;i institu&#355;iile publice prev&#259;zute la art. 369 lit. b) a\ncompeten&#355;elor generale necesare ocup&#259;rii unei func&#355;ii publice de\nconducere în cadrul concursului de promovare prev&#259;zut la alin. (8), în\nalte situa&#355;ii decât cea prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (9), se\nutilizeaz&#259; platforma informatic&#259; de concurs în condi&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 467<sup>1</sup> alin. (2).</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}